  "text": "Tryptamine psychedelics such as psilocybin are known to alter perception, mood, and a host of cognitive processes (Nichols 2004 ) and have been indicated for the treatment of mood disorders [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Additionally, classical serotonergic hallucinogens such as LSD or psilocybin are considered physiologically safe and do not produce dependence or addiction (Nichols 2004) . A similar potential might exist for the short-acting tryptamine 5-methoxy-N,N-dimethyltryptamine (5-MeO-DMT).",
